org.datavec.api.transform.schema

Class Schema

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.transform.schema.Schema
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SequenceSchema

    public class Schema
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A Schema defines the layout of tabular data. Specifically, it contains names for each column, as well as details of types (Integer, String, Long, Double, etc).
    Type information for each column may optionally include restrictions on the allowable values for each column.

    See also: SequenceSchema
